have a lawyer?

864
00:46:19,148 --> 00:46:20,568
No, we don't have
a lawyer.

865
00:46:20,609 --> 00:46:23,405
There's a guy, there's a guy
in Racine. His name is...

866
00:46:23,448 --> 00:46:24,825
...is Reverdy.
Theresa knows him.

867
00:46:24,866 --> 00:46:26,619
He's supposed to be
the best, okay?

868
00:46:26,661 --> 00:46:27,705
Call him!

869
00:46:27,746 --> 00:46:29,458
[chatter, gravel scrapes]

870
00:46:30,585 --> 00:46:32,087
Officer, is there somebody
I can call?

871
00:46:32,129 --> 00:46:33,422
Wh- who do I call?

872
00:46:33,465 --> 00:46:35,051
[Claire crying,
doors thud shut]

873
00:46:35,092 --> 00:46:37,346
[engine turns over]

874
00:46:49,409 --> 00:46:50,244
Alice!

875
00:46:51,496 --> 00:46:52,915
[Emma panting]
Alice, wh-

876
00:46:52,957 --> 00:46:54,709
Come here. Come here!

877
00:46:54,752 --> 00:46:59,259
[gravel scraping]

878
00:47:06,731 --> 00:47:09,109
[phone rings]

879
00:47:12,073 --> 00:47:14,536
[phone rings]
Daddy!

880
00:47:17,041 --> 00:47:19,252
[phone rings]

881
00:47:22,258 --> 00:47:24,428
[phone rings]

882
00:47:24,469 --> 00:47:26,265
[Emma groans in pain]

883
00:47:26,306 --> 00:47:28,268
- Hello?
