heard about Alice.

1040
00:53:43,669 --> 00:53:46,091
Uh, if you could watch
Emma and Claire,

1041
00:53:46,132 --> 00:53:47,468
on Sunday, around uh...

1042
00:53:47,509 --> 00:53:49,429
[woman] Oh, I don't think so.

1043
00:53:49,471 --> 00:53:51,767
And if you'll excuse me,
I'm just on my way
out the door.

1044
00:53:53,395 --> 00:53:55,189
